<h2><span style=3D"font-size:20px;"><b>INJECTOR FLOW VS PRESSURE CHANGE CAL=
CULATOR</b></span></h2> <br> <p>Sometimes, getting the exact right size inj=
ectors is not possible, or you make some minor engine mods, only to find th=
at your injectors are too small.</p> <br> <p>You can use this calculator to=
 determine how much more flow your injectors can deliver&nbsp;</p> <br> <p>=
<b>Do not go crazy on the New Fuel Pressure value.</b> The rest of your fue=
l system will only work up to a certain pressure based on your fuel pump, f=
ilters, regulator and fuel lines.</p> <br> <p>If you are looking to get mor=
e than 15% extra fuel flow out of your injectors, you might well run into o=
ther fuel system limitations, which can cause inconsistent fuel delivery, a=
nd be hazardous to your engine.&nbsp;&nbsp;<b style=3D"font-family: Lato, s=
ans-serif;">At this point, it's important to talk to someone with the exper=
ience to guide you through this process.</b></p> <br> <hr> <p><b>NOTES:</b>=
</p> <p><br>- The PSI/Bar selector operates both the Old Fuel Pressure and =
New Fuel Pressure values.</p></div><div>


<div class=3D"efi-calc">
	<h3>Injector Flow Vs Pressure Calculator</h3>

	<div class=3D"input-row">
		<label>Injector Flow Rate:</label>
		<input id=3D"injector_flow" type=3D"number" value=3D"500" min=3D"1">
		<select id=3D"flow_unit">
			<option value=3D"cc">CC/min</option>
			<option value=3D"lb">LB/hr</option>
		</select>
	</div>

	<div class=3D"input-row">
		<label>Old Fuel Pressure:</label>
		<input id=3D"old_pressure" type=3D"number" value=3D"43.5" min=3D"1">
		<select id=3D"pressure_unit">
			<option value=3D"psi">PSI</option>
			<option value=3D"bar">Bar</option>
		</select>
	</div>
	<div class=3D"input-row">
		<label>New Fuel Pressure:</label>
		<input id=3D"new_pressure" type=3D"number" value=3D"58" min=3D"1">
                <span style=3D"visibility:hidden; width:120px;"></span>
	</div>

	<button id=3D"calc_btn">Calculate New Flow Rate</button>

	<div class=3D"results">
		<div class=3D"results-row">
			<span class=3D"result-label">New Flow Rate (CC/min):</span>
			<span class=3D"result-value" id=3D"calc_new_cc">0</span>
		</div>
		<div class=3D"results-row">
			<span class=3D"result-label">New Flow Rate (LB/hr):</span>
			<span class=3D"result-value" id=3D"calc_new_lb">0</span>
		</div>
		<div class=3D"results-row">
			<span class=3D"result-label">Percentage Change (%):</span>
			<span class=3D"result-value" id=3D"calc_percentage">0</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


